Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:04.49,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23rd - Summer Break\N25th - Summer School Starts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,x becomes 4. Substitute this value in the\Nformula to calculate the value of y.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can derive the coordinates at the\Ntop, enabling you to draw a graph.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.51,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31st - Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing what I'm supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were playing reluctantly! It\Nsounded like your heart wasn't in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... Do we have to play\Nthis piece for the gala concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a gala concert, we should be\Nplaying something more glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change it to\Nsomething more major...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This is the\Nsong I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry. If you and I\Nplay it, it will sound glamorous enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why you're\Nso reluctant to play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the score was overflowing\Nwith so much love for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kreisler's... Love's Joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love's... Sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love's Sorrow, the companion piece to Love's\NJoy by Kreisler, was written for the violin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a piano version of this\Nsong arranged by Rachmaninoff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I stick it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Falling asleep under the piano again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten heavy, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The piano isn't responding to you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you would just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hear! Help me, Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why you're\Nso reluctant to play it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because it reminds me of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko-san, I've got to practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No sweat, no sweat! It's good to have\Na change of scenery, to take a breather!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton candy! Frappes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get lost on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rachmaninoff's Love's Sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki used to play that all the\Ntime since we were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She used to play it a lot as a lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This piece just reeks too much of my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So raw... and vivid... It closes in on me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mother must've\Nhad despised me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No mother on earth\Ndespises her own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was the moment you grew up,\Nboth as a person and as a pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that\Nwouldn't make Saki happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it is just a little\Nbit sad, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To see your kid grow away from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she'll forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For trying so hard to forget all about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for me\Nto play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you feel, play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something holding you\Nback, then play with conviction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and try to hear Saki's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't sit there brooding over ridiculous matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's high time you manned up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play. You and I are\Npianists, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A candy apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like candy apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that. It's just that\NI've never had one before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry! I'll eat it!\NI'll eat it, okay? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I being too harsh with\Nhim? But he's got to play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that he can\Nmature as a pianist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that he can say goodbye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.43,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31st - Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look how late it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because you\Nwouldn't give up. What a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, you\Nkept whining about the piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're so late coming home,\NI wonder if your folks are mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look up there! At the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are so beautiful.\NIt's like the stars are speaking to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, little star,\Nhow I wonder what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Up above the world so high,\N like a diamond in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, little star,\Nhow I wonder what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if it isn't Arima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are just leftovers,\Nbut have your fill, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got some test samples, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I've already had more than enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are fans of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, they\Ncame to hear you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard all about it, Arima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't abort your performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's like flushing all your\Nstruggles till now down the drain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like baking a\Nmoist sponge cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,only for it to be totally ruined\Nby some horrible-tasting cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I like a young man\Nwho does the unheard-of!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's inside your stomach,\Nthere's no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the ingredients are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see some pictures of\NKaori back in grade school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have some from\Nkindergarten, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, for your folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much. And\Nthank you for all the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going to the gala\Nconcert to cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you to the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Arima-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's got manners, and he's\Na good kid, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really! They even hauled out\Nthe pictures of me as a newborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stark naked, no less! I can\Nnever get married now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have cheerful parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's always stuffing\Nstarving dogs with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starving?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you get taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. It's because you're\Nnot looking down anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it sure is hot this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A meaningless conversation.\NFamiliar scenery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so humid! It's so deplorable,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's really muggy, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, the reason I remember\Nit so well is probably...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I do like summer\Nbecause there are fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'm sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...because of that summer night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:03.57,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31st - Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...told...you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make that part flow more elegantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the accompanist can't\Njust ignore instructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or else the violin won't stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It will too stand out!\NBecause I'm gonna be playing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're so arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Follow what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my green tea\Nand red bean shaved ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's not that simple!\NYou runaway horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was my shaved ice! I've had enough!\NI don't want to go to summer school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the festival!\NI want to watch fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The year's first fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure we won't get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sneaking into the pool area\Nand lighting firecrackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the teachers have\Nall gone home anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And as for water, we've got a\Nwhole boatload at our disposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But lay off the rockets, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kashiwagi-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! Summer\Nschool again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just suck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for being a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you lousy\Nscholarship student!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean high school. You're not\Nattending summer school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so does that mean you two\Nare on the music college track?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...not even thinking about the future yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let me just say that I'm\Ngoing to rock the audience at the gala,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and claim the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're the\Nalmighty duo, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit,\Nthat's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... those two look great together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gaping at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's totally dark at the bottom...\N I can't hear a sound...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me... please help me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hear anything.\NIt's dark... it's dark...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that you can't\Nhear the notes means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that you're not bound\Nby auditory sounds, I think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not bound by sound?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The images you have within you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sounds that rise up\Nfrom the bottom of your soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've been letting them\Noverride all else without realizing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sounds within you,\Nthe imagined scenery...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wasn't there ever a\Nmoment when you sensed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the notes suffused\Nwith your desires and emotions?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Losing the ability to hear the\Nnotes. I'm sure that that's a gift.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A gift?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, cover your ears,\Nand play as you feel for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have the technical\Nability to pull that off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ability to trace the sounds within\Nyou, the sounds you imagine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And those are the memories Saki left you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you get taller?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because you're not\Nlooking down anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's because you're\Nlooking up now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's proof that he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you drown in such a shallow pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's gonna blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He freakin' slammed his head\Nright into his savior's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it because it's a pool?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it because the moon's out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:16:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe... just maybe, the light can\Nreach even the bottom of a dark ocean.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.99,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31st - Gala Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miyazono-san's playing, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that kid who\Nstopped playing midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people who run this\Nare reckless for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll actually\Nmake an impact. Can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if she'll play it right today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll probably go bonkers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I came today just to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:30.69,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curse
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! There's nobody\NI know around here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to take your seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Ochiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... did you call me Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who told you about\NArima-kun being an accompanist today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-Not that I came here to see Arima...\NI'm just here to enjoy some violin music...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. It'll be starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You witch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No judging at gala concerts, so we can\Njust sit back and enjoy ourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this level of talent, we can certainly\Nafford to listen like everyone else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, is it almost\Ntime for my favorite?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:15.27,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono\NSumitani Junior Highschool
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does she think she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The violinist a no-show?\NThat's just insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she, Michelangeli? Pogoreli?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The show's started.\NKao-chan's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kaori Miyazono this unpredictable?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling her cell,\Nbut she's totally not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.38,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious. I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in and get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll be ready whenever\NMiyazono does show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, keep calling Miyazono's cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ask if they'll move\Nyou guys down in the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's a gala concert, they\Nmight be a little more flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we can get\Nthe performers to agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can wait on Miyazono\Ntill the last possible second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't pan out,\Nwe'll just have to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the song I want to play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Weren't you looking\Nforward to this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was an idiot for\Ngetting carried away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Kaori Miyazono's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what she's going to do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while since\NI've felt this excited.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please! She's on a bus\Nright now, on her way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may,\N I don't have the authority to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miike-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miike-kun... He's the final\Nact of the junior high division?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, being that\Nhe won the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you\Nlet them play after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our violinist's running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Running late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Kaori Miyazono.\NI'm sure she'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think you could\Nlet her play after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miyazono-san's playing, too, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The final act of this gala concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The starring role... it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is your moment of triumph, after all.\NWe only have ourselves to blame.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for being so presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're going\Nto have to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's her own fault for being\Nlate on a day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her playing's such a mess, no wonder\Nher lifestyle's all messed up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks she's special just because\Nthe audience kind of liked her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so she shows up late\Nwithout a second thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The music is written in the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What she produces is disastrous.\NIt's not music or anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat, who are\Nyou to talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Sorry for causing\Na disturbance before you perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kousei,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you pissed at all?\NHe insulted your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go by the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please perform the final act of\Nthe junior high division, Miike-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The spotlight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today's spotlight belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The promoters' choice for the junior\Nhigh division, Ms. Kaori Miyazono.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miyazono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She got here in time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kaori Miyazono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he the accompanist?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the violinist?\NWhere's Miyazono-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima, surely you're not playing alone...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unprecedented.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.96,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle Little Star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:43.66,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13\NLove's Sadness
